1
00:00:32,299 --> 00:00:33,230
Ying Wujiu.

2
00:00:33,900 --> 00:00:35,300
You fool.

3
00:00:35,660 --> 00:00:37,200
Am I worth it?

4
00:00:37,660 --> 00:00:38,800
Reborn to this life,

5
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:39,960
just to protect me,

6
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:42,230
you even took that knife,

7
00:00:42,630 --> 00:00:44,460
making yourself a crippled man.

8
00:00:45,030 --> 00:00:46,430
Why are you so silly?

9
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:50,630
You ruined both of your lives for me.

10
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,630
How can I ever repay you?

11
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:54,260
Ying Wujiu.

12
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:55,500
In this life,

13
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:57,700
I won't let you die a tragic death for me.

14
00:00:58,100 --> 00:00:59,500
It's my turn to protect you.

15
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:00,030
Jingzhi,

16
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:01,260
don't cry.

17
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,099
I am a whole man in this life.

18
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:06,000
I forged that file.

19
00:01:06,260 --> 00:01:07,630
Once the secret is out,

20
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:10,830
Yu Henian and Helan Ci will tear us to pieces.

21
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:12,560
To protect you,

22
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:14,400
I had to make you hate me.

23
00:01:14,730 --> 00:01:16,460
That little wench who slipped in just now

24
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:17,800
is quite a beauty.

25
00:01:17,900 --> 00:01:19,600
When the Director is done with her and rewards us,

26
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:21,760
we brothers can take her back and have some fun.

27
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:23,360
Though we lack that certain something,

28
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,960
we have plenty of ways to torture a woman.

29
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:25,900
Drip boiling chili oil,

30
00:01:25,900 --> 00:01:26,630
prick her with silver needles,

31
00:01:26,630 --> 00:01:28,500
and listen to her cry and beg on the bed.

32
00:01:28,500 --> 00:01:30,060
Once she's in our hands,

33
00:01:30,060 --> 00:01:31,720
we'll make her wish for death.

34
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,600
In this deep palace,

35
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:45,060
even if a speck of dust falls on her,

36
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:47,830
I will grind your bones to dust.

37
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,030
Jingzhi, in this life,

38
00:01:50,030 --> 00:01:52,160
I only wish you peace and safety.

39
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,229
But what you have to face

40
00:01:53,229 --> 00:01:55,830
is the craziest dragon in the Dazheng Dynasty.

41
00:01:55,830 --> 00:01:57,300
Are you ready?

42
00:01:57,560 --> 00:02:00,600
Get out, all of you!

43
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:05,860
Who let you in?

44
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,030
I said whoever dares to see me go mad,

45
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:09,400
I'll gouge their eyes out.

46
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,660
Right now, you only see slaughter, Your Majesty.

47
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:13,260
But in my eyes, Your Majesty,

48
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:15,430
you're just a poor man dying of pain.

49
00:02:15,430 --> 00:02:17,000
If you want to cure your headache, Your Majesty,

50
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,200
you must listen to me.

51
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:19,860
When I apply the needles,

52
00:02:19,860 --> 00:02:21,700
you must tie your own hands, Your Majesty,

53
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:23,300
lest you accidentally hurt me when you go mad.

54
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:24,700
Tie my own hands?

55
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:26,430
The whole world wants to kill me.

56
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:28,300
A lowly servant from the Yeting Bureau like you

57
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:30,300
dares to ask me to hand my life over to you?

58
00:02:30,300 --> 00:02:31,230
Hahahaha!

59
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,130
I've killed so many people.

60
00:02:36,230 --> 00:02:37,100
You are the first one

61
00:02:37,100 --> 00:02:38,700
who dares to tie me up with a rope

62
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:40,900
and actually make me feel comfortable.

63
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:45,100
I know you were sent by the Yu family.

64
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:47,160
Fine, since you're useful,

65
00:02:47,260 --> 00:02:48,460
I'll take you.

66
00:02:48,829 --> 00:02:50,800
I grant you this gold medal.

67
00:02:50,900 --> 00:02:52,030
From now on, whenever I have a headache,

68
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:53,400
get your ass to my bed.

69
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:54,700
If you dare not to come,

70
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:56,900
I'll kill everyone in the Yeting Bureau.

71
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:58,100
Feel the pain with me.

72
00:02:58,260 --> 00:03:00,600
Helan Ci, you granted her the gold medal.

73
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:02,460
Did you want to lock her in a cage?

74
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:04,500
You will never know, these past three years,

75
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:07,100
whose name she called out in the water dungeon.

76
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:08,830
Jingzhi.

77
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:10,800
Only when you are by my side,

78
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,060
does this bedchamber not feel like a tomb.

79
00:03:13,060 --> 00:03:14,030
Raise your head.

80
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,230
When did my bedchamber

81
00:03:15,230 --> 00:03:17,500
become a place for you to stare at your toes?

82
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,960
I dare not profane Your Majesty.

83
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,860
Please, Your Majesty,

84
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:21,260
allow me to leave the tea and withdraw.

85
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:23,829
I have given you the greatest splendor in the world,

86
00:03:23,829 --> 00:03:26,090
even allowing you to not kneel before me.

87
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:26,829
Yet you,

88
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,960
why do you never look me in the eye?

89
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:30,760
Just nod,

90
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:32,360
and I will depose the empress

91
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,760
and let you rule the inner palace.

92
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,600
Your Majesty is a solitary dragon high in the sky,

93
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:37,300
and I am a withered lotus in the mire.

94
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:38,100
Your Majesty's misplaced love

95
00:03:38,100 --> 00:03:39,500
is only because your head doesn't ache right now

96
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:40,300
and your heart is idle.

97
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:41,500
If I truly nod,

98
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:42,860
once Your Majesty tires of this medicine,

99
00:03:42,860 --> 00:03:44,460
I will only become

100
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:45,329
another nameless skeleton in a dry well of this deep palace.

101
00:03:45,329 --> 00:03:46,600
I am talking to you about love,

102
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:47,860
and you are fortune-telling with me.

103
00:03:47,860 --> 00:03:48,660
Qu Jingzhi,

104
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:50,260
who exactly are you

105
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,890
waiting for through me?

106
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,829
Did he touch you?

107
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:03,100
I am asking you,

108
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:04,100
where did he touch you?

109
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:05,730
You are interfering too much.

110
00:04:05,730 --> 00:04:08,460
I was sent by the Prime Minister to serve the Emperor.

111
00:04:08,460 --> 00:04:10,000
Wherever the Emperor wants to touch,

112
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,100
I will just endure it.

113
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:12,230
Say that again.

114
00:04:12,260 --> 00:04:12,930
Do you know

115
00:04:12,930 --> 00:04:15,100
that Helan Ci is a complete lunatic?

116
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:17,630
He even hides a knife under his pillow.

117
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:21,160
Do you really think you can survive on those few silver needles?

118
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:29,020
It's still very dangerous right now,

119
00:04:29,060 --> 00:04:31,030
there are spies everywhere.

120
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:33,060
Ying Wujiu, listen carefully.

121
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:34,990
I don't care if you are a eunuch now,

122
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,300
nor do I care what inhuman torture you suffered

123
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:37,760
to climb to this position.

124
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,700
From now on,

125
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:39,900
your life is mine.

126
00:04:40,060 --> 00:04:41,700
I am claiming you.

127
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:42,860
If the Emperor tries to touch me,

128
00:04:42,860 --> 00:04:43,800
I will kill him.

129
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:45,000
If Yu Henian tries to harm you,

130
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,200
I will slaughter his entire family.
